    "Manual parameter search for EfficientNet-GRUSimilarly, Table 6 comprises the hyperparameters that were determined to be the most optimal ones for the Effi-cientNet-GRU architecture for the combined dataset.Both the EfficientNet and EfficientNet-GRU networks equipped with manually selected best model configurations are subsequently evaluated using test sets of Celeb-DFv2, DFDC and the combined datasets, respectively.",
